@node "whatis" "What is AppTemp?"
>>>>>>>>>> What is AppTemp?

   AppTemp is an application template generator.  Fill in the fields in
   the main window.  Then fill in the fields for the window from the
   Objects/Windows window.  Now use the menus to Make Source or Save the
   project.

   ***** NOTE: This program generates source code in the "OLD" MUI
               format.  See "psi.c" source included in MUI 3 for more
               information on the preferred object-oriented programming
               methodology.  AppTemp will be dramatically updated in
               the future.  Project file compatability is not a
               guarantee.  However, this program may still be useful
               for some people.
@endnode

@node "useful" "How's this useful?"
>>>>>>>>>> How's this useful?

   It makes easy and quick setup of the base of an application.
   The AppTemp.Dat file is editable so you can customize the source code
   to your particular needs.
@endnode

